{"tid":1182781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇到蜜蜂你會點？","createTime":"2019-06-02T12:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T12:27:17.000Z","uid":202120,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7204b04c00f327c508741b73e646d776e04bfb67","tid":1182781,"uid":202120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"我就會跑走，自細好驚昆蟲<br />\n因為小學嗰陣跟小童群益會去啲有機農場<br />\n啲職員教有蜜蜂只要企係到就冇事<br />\n之後有個同學仔見到蜜蜂企咗係到<br />\n屌你老母親眼見到隻蜜蜂行入佢耳窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n企佢老母咩 自始見到蜜蜂一定急步行或者跑走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱呀梗係跑走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老系都企係到"},{"pid":"8481b8fcabeb9e4e441958aead0a35caa2ccfae3","tid":1182781,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"遲過比蜜蜂針過一次  又暈又嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba372d8c1b7c5722836ca3d93f00435edfc0cbd1","tid":1182781,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8481b8fcabeb9e4e441958aead0a35caa2ccfae3","tid":1182781,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"遲過比蜜蜂針過一次  又暈又嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"試過"},{"pid":"59ce50ac3d66802d3e6d0db692d46774552ded07","tid":1182781,"uid":134546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"津路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2b2afe028f78b5959d308e666de487717ce648","tid":1182781,"uid":202120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8481b8fcabeb9e4e441958aead0a35caa2ccfae3","tid":1182781,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"遲過比蜜蜂針過一次  又暈又嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,